If linux said when you want change the password to the one you used before,directly change do not work.It will show below error
3004-314 Password was recently used and is not valid for reuse.

Below will be worked:
1.change the password to another new password:   #passwd  came(username)
2.change the password to the second new password:#passwd  came(username)
3.change the password to the third new password:#passwd  came(username)
4.change the password to the password you want:#passwd  came(username)
end
